                "invention-title": [
                    "Central heating type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor",
                    "一种中心加热式沼气重整制氢反应器"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a central heating type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor. The reforming hydrogen production reactor comprises a reactor shell, a reaction tube and a combustor. Raw material gas enters the reaction tube from the gas inlet tube, is subjected to reforming reaction under the action of a catalyst to generate hydrogen, and is discharged from the gas outlet tube; a combustor is arranged in the center of the reforming hydrogen production reactor, high-temperature flue gas generated by combustion of fuel gas directly heats reaction tubes around the combustor, the heat transfer efficiency is high, the flue gas after heat exchange rebounds through a furnace wall at the bottom of the reactor, flows back and rises to a flue gas outlet in the side wall above the reactor and then is exhausted, and the flue gas energy utilization rate is further increased; a catalyst discharge pipe is arranged at the bottom of the reaction pipe, so that catalyst discharge is facilitated; a groove is formed in the bottom of the reactor shell, and a catalyst discharging space is provided, so that the reactor space is saved; the hydrogen production reactor is compact in structure, convenient to disassemble and assemble, uniform in heating in the reactor, high in heat exchange efficiency and capable of efficiently achieving the reforming hydrogen production reaction process."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种中心加热式沼气重整制氢反应器。所述重整制氢反应器包括反应器壳体、反应管和燃烧器。原料气从进气管进入反应管，在催化剂的作用下发生重整反应生成氢气后由出气管排出；重整制氢反应器中心位置布置燃烧器，燃气燃烧产生的高温烟气直接加热燃烧器周围的反应管，传热效率高，换热后烟气经反应器底部炉墙反弹回流上升至反应器上方侧壁的烟气出口后排出，进一步提高烟气能量利用率；反应管底部设置催化剂卸放管，便于催化剂卸放；反应器壳体底部设置凹槽，并提供催化剂卸放的空间，节省反应器空间；该制氢反应器结构紧凑、拆装方便，反应器内部受热均匀、换热效率高，能够高效实现重整制氢反应过程。"
                }
            ]
